    </div>

    <div class="form-card">
        <h2>SIFO-referansetabeller <span class="page-sub" style="font-weight:400">(fra Beregningsmodell.xlsx)</span></h2>
        <h3 style="margin:14px 0 6px">Individkostnad pr. mnd — sum 1-5 (mat, klær, helse, fritid, reise)</h3>
